            <h3 class="icon_question">
                Where To Buy?</h3>
            School wear can be bought from the school office. The school office is situated
            at the National School at Tabuan Desa. It sells an assortment of school bags and
            uniform items.
            <p>
                The school uniform can be ordered from the school appointed tailor.</p>
        </div>
        <p>
            The school puts great emphasis on the wearing of the school uniform and the need
            for all students to take pride in their appearance.</p>
        <p>
            The wearing of jewellery is prohibited at school with the exception of a wrist watch
            and ear studs for those students with pierced ears. Students are permitted to wear
            a necklace only if it is of religious significance. Make up and nail polish are
            strictly prohibited. Girls with long hair must wear it tied back and students are
            not permitted to wear hair colourings or extreme hair styles</p>
        <p class="icon_note ml20 mt20 mb20">
            Please note that white shoes and socks are to be worn with the Kindy, Primary and
            Secondary school uniforms.</p>
